{
  "stem": "11723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't take my Grandfather Katz because my Grandfather Katz was disabled.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father, however, was very lucky, in a sense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he decided that he was going to no camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was not going to any camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And essentially, this was not a camp on the scale of Bergen-Belsen or any of those camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These were units attached to the regular Hungarian Army which performed slave labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had to provide their own uniforms, and they had to wear a yellow armband and-- just to signify they were Jews-- and they got much smaller rations.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some of them were lucky and were treated well by their army officers, and some of them were not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, my father, as I said, he was on the train, being taken out of the country, and he just didn't want to leave.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And while the train was passing through a wheat field, he jumped off, and he hid in the wheat field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow under the cover of darkness, he made his way home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my grandmother got into action.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father had a schoolmate whose name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lehodski.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a neurologist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Grandma and my father went to him and said, can you give him a certificate that he's not normal?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they didn't take people to slave labor who weren't quite right up there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so he gave my father the certificate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the meantime, in 19-- the end of 1942-- because he was taken earlier in 1942, and then he escaped-- end of 1942, my sister was born.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometime early in 1943, they came for him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that point, my mother went to open the door so that the two officers are there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
